ygData.subject: RE: Wakishi quest
ygData.msgSnippet: Yes Lord Grimlot gives you nothing back for the Lute, he equips it when you give it to him.  That is not the Wakizashi quest. Shada Silverleaf, Level 50 Bard,
ygData.messageBody:
Yes Lord Grimlot gives you nothing back for the Lute, he equips it when you
give it to him. That is not the Wakizashi quest.

Shada Silverleaf, Level 50 Bard, Mithaniel Marr
Erisi, Level 12 Paladin, Mithaniel Marr
